30.content:
The rabbit's carrot is missing, so it went to report to Sheriff Black Cat. Sheriff Black Cat ultimately identified four animals: a fox, a tiger, a lion, and a wolf. The criminal is among them.
The fox said: "I didn't steal the carrot.";
The tiger said: "The wolf stole the carrot.";
The lion said: "The tiger stole the carrot.";
The wolf said: "I have never stolen a carrot."
After investigation, it was found that only one of the four animals is telling the truth. Who stole the carrot?

46.content:
