(1) Xiao Qiang is not a contestant from school A;
(2) Xiao Ming is not a contestant from school B;
(3) The contestant from school A did not win the first prize;
(4) The contestant from school B won the second prize;
(5) Xiao Ming did not win the third prize.
Based on the above information, can you determine which school Xiao Yong is from and what prize he won?

